INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [dto.ProductCategory0] ON [x.Publisher.Products].[CategoryId] = [dto.ProductCategory0].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x2].[DateCreated], [x2].[Id], [x.Publisher2].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [Products] AS [x2]
    INNER JOIN [Publishers] AS [x.Publisher2] ON [x2].[PublisherId] = [x.Publisher2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Authors] AS [x.Author2] ON [x2].[AuthorId] = [x.Author2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.ProductCategory2] ON [x2].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory2].[Id]
    WHERE [x2].[Status] = 1
    ORDER BY [x2].[DateCreated] DESC, [x2].[Id], [x.Publisher2].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1] ON [x.Publisher.Products].[PublisherId] = [t1].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t1].[DateCreated] DESC, [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)
